smart-mode-line.el is a ModeLineConfiguration package which makes the ModeLine sexy and super powered. 

What super powers? Well... smart truncation of directories and minor modes, of course! Not to mention prefixes, full/fixed/flexible width, easy customization, and being super sexy. 

http://bruce-connor.github.com/control-pianobar/sml/sml-small.png

The primary focus of these features is to convey *as much information* as possible in the most *space efficient* way possible. 

For more details on these features, see its github page:
https://github.com/Bruce-Connor/smart-mode-line/

=== Download ===
The latest version is always available on Melpa and on the github page. Direct link here: 
https://github.com/Bruce-Connor/smart-mode-line/blob/master/smart-mode-line.el

